                        "description":  "Choose bones or a corpse of a Medium or Small Humanoid within 10 feet to create a Skeleton or Zombie. For 24 hours, you can mentally command any Undead animated by this spell within 60 feet as a Bonus Action, issuing the same command to multiple controlled Undead; without commands they Dodge and move only to avoid harm, orders continue until complete, control stops after 24 hours unless recast before expiry, and higher slots animate or reassert control over two additional Undead per slot level above 3.",
